<p>This site was created to honor my late husband, Bob, who lost his fight with esophageal cancer in October 2009.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<em>Cancer Spoken Here </em>is a book and a website. The book is a memoir about how our family had an open and honest dialogue about cancer with two young children, knowing our time together was precious and limited.<br />
<br />
T-shirts, baseball caps, and wristbands&nbsp;are available for purchase by emailing me. They proudly display the trademark, <em>Cancer Spoken Here</em>. The site will expand its ecommerce page to include additional apparel, jewelry, and other items by January 1, 2012.<br />
<br />
I hope that everyone reading this can reach out to someone with cancer, spread the word to help those in need, and make everyone fighting this disease a survivor.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
